<%# Phase 7.5 §11i — "in sync" banner partial.

    Rendered inside the `channel_diff_banner` Turbo Frame after a
    user-triggered diff check finds no divergence. The empty branch
    of the broadcast: replaces any stale open-diff banner with this
    transient notice, signalling the diff-check finished without
    finding anything to resolve. The frame still exists; the next
    cron pass (or another `[sync]`) can refill it.

    Locals:
      - channel: the Channel the sync ran against
%>
<%= turbo_frame_tag "channel_diff_banner" do %>
  <div class="pane pane--standalone text-muted"
       style="margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 6px 10px;">
    in sync with youtube.
  </div>
<% end %>
